data.value:
String to add to the end of each message
                                Available macros:
                                @@appname - application name;
                                @@version - application version;
                                @@subversion - application subversion;
                                @@build - application build;
                                @@copyright - copyright string;
                                @@nick - your nick name;
                                @@osname - OS name;
                                @@osversion - OS version;
